name: PHOENIX
description:
"You've suffered for so long,
Your efforts go unrewarded,
The world stays indifferent.

You've lost your way,
Bitter and resentful,
The flame that was once your passion,
has become the instrument of your destruction.

But something would not give,
despite having every reason to end it all,
you chose to hold on.

And from the depths of despair a small flame emerges,
not scorching, but warm and kind.

The fire of life.

Now rise, dust off the ashes,
you are, phoenix."
